<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.4">
<l>vaṇṇak karuṅkuḻal mātar vantalar tūṟṟiṭa</l>
<l>paṇṇip palaceytip pāṭiyeṅ kumtiri yāmē</l>
<l>kaṇṇuk kiṉiyāṉaik kāṉata riṭaikkaṉ ṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>eṇṇaṟ kariyāṉaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To stop him from wandering everywhere in this village,</l>
<l rend="indent">doing many things,</l>
<l>So that ladies with beautiful black curls come to spread gossip</l>
<l rend="indent">after the claves on the forest path.</l>
<l>Ah! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
